snippet: Fourth-seeded Roger Federer ended top-seeded Novak Djokovic’s chance of defending his Dubai Championships title with a semifinal win Friday.
abstract: Roger Federer defeats Novak Djokovic in Dubai Championships men's semifinal; will face Tomas Berdych in final.
lead_paragraph: Fourth-seeded Roger Federer ended top-seeded Novak Djokovic’s chance of defending his Dubai Championships title with a semifinal win Friday.
